%sh
# Add header to sam file
docker run -v /var/zeppelin-notebooks/disk:/notebooks/disk mcapuccini/alignment:latest sh -c \
    "cat /ref/human_g1k_v37.dict /notebooks/disk/aln.sam > /notebooks/disk/aln.header.sam"
# Took 4 min 45 sec

%sh
# Add RG
docker run -v /var/zeppelin-notebooks/disk:/notebooks/disk mcapuccini/alignment:latest sh -c "gatk AddOrReplaceReadGroups --INPUT=/notebooks/disk/aln.header.sam --OUTPUT=/notebooks/disk/aln.header.sorted.rg.bam --SORT_ORDER=coordinate --RGID=HG02666-id --RGLB=HG02666-lib --RGPL=ILLUMINA --RGPU=HG02666-01 --RGSM=HG02666"
# Took 1 hrs 35 min 46 sec
